}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#52caa1a6b2cdcf88c2ae8e2e96ec6f18>.
<#52caa1a6b2cdcf88c2ae8e2e96ec6f18> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2cb9200d-57a3-4068-8157-5706fd0c587b>;
