_:b0__34351 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.20 69.10,26.10 69.10,26.10 55.00,11.20 55.00,11.20 69.10))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
