_:b0__80975 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((11.23 69.08,24.14 69.08,24.14 55.02,11.23 55.02,11.23 69.08))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
