_:b0__83115 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((-4.10 65.90,30.20 65.90,30.20 48.50,-4.10 48.50,-4.10 65.90))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
