<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2f208eba36e50dac9295e7f62aed9c00>.
<#2f208eba36e50dac9295e7f62aed9c00> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://resources.stockholm.se/data/595a2dd0-b0dd-47d6-a953-fd75b9fd31c1>;
